00:00:16.433 --> 00:00:19.811 position:50% align:center
The Kouka Revue was
founded in the Taisho era

00:00:19.811 --> 00:00:25.609 position:50% align:center
by Ooizumi Minoru, part of a group of
big-name companies in Kobe.

00:00:25.609 --> 00:00:28.737 position:50% align:center
The all-female acting troupe was
comprised of young, unmarried women.

00:00:28.737 --> 00:00:31.949 position:50% align:center line:10%
"The Rose of Versailles"

00:00:32.074 --> 00:00:36.161 position:50% align:center
Their extravagant productions
stole the hearts of thousands.

00:00:37.120 --> 00:00:38.747 position:50% align:center
None moreso than their
<i>otoko-yaku </i>actresses,

00:00:38.747 --> 00:00:41.875 position:50% align:center
who were said to be more
gentlemanly than 'real' men,

00:00:41.875 --> 00:00:44.920 position:50% align:center
and earned the troupe
huge swaths of female fans.

00:00:44.920 --> 00:00:49.049 position:50% align:center
Years later, they established a school
to train the troupe's next big stars,

00:00:49.049 --> 00:00:52.761 position:50% align:center
the Kouka School of
Musical and Theatrical Arts.

00:00:52.761 --> 00:00:56.348 position:50% align:center
Its admittance rate is
as low as Tokyo University,

00:00:56.348 --> 00:01:00.394 position:50% align:center
with only the most lovely and
talented actresses offered admission.

00:02:37.241 --> 00:02:40.118 position:50% align:center line:10%
"Beneath the Cherry Tree,
in a Rain of Petals"

00:03:13.485 --> 00:03:16.113 position:50% align:center
Excuse me, are you...

00:03:24.663 --> 00:03:26.331 position:50% align:center
Naracchi?

00:03:39.178 --> 00:03:43.056 position:50% align:center
You're Naracchi from JPX, right?!

00:03:43.056 --> 00:03:48.061 position:50% align:center
Oh, sorry to bother you!
I'm just such a <i>huge </i>Naracchi stan!

00:03:48.061 --> 00:03:50.606 position:50% align:center
I'm so sorry they made you
graduate like that,

00:03:50.606 --> 00:03:54.735 position:50% align:center
but I really hope you'll
keep giving it your all!

00:03:54.735 --> 00:03:59.907 position:50% align:center
I'll stan you forever, Naracchi!
I can't wait to see what you do next!

00:03:59.907 --> 00:04:02.743 position:50% align:center
No! I'm scared! Someone, help!

00:04:03.660 --> 00:04:04.536 position:50% align:center
