00:04:19.718 --> 00:04:20.969 position:50% align:center
Oh.

00:04:21.929 --> 00:04:24.848 position:50% align:center
Don't worry, he didn't follow you.

00:04:24.848 --> 00:04:27.017 position:50% align:center
